    "John Trapp": "Christ is all, and in all ] Not only in t he hearts of men, but in all things else, \u03b5\u03bd \u03c0\u03b1\u03c3\u03b9, in the neuter gender. This second Adam `[char_Adam_Luk_3]` hath filled all things again; neither is there anything else required to justification and salvation.\nVer.\n11. Christ is all, and in all] Not only in the hearts of men, but in all things else, \u03b5\u03bd \u03c0\u03b1\u03c3\u03b9, in the neuter gender. This second Adam `[char_Adam_Luk_3]` hath filled all things again; neither is there anything else required to justification and salvation.\nVer."
